{"tid":2389872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本爆紅  IKEA玩具用心歹毒？","createTime":"2021-02-01T07:58:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T16:31:29.000Z","uid":184679,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9c12f162bd10d8154ddb4c80597f586f6e00e230","tid":2389872,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T07:58:48.000Z","msg":"IKEA全新超人氣玩偶來了！在日本推特引起超高討論度的「棕熊填充玩具」，大尺寸配上厭世神情，完全是被工作榨乾的我們啊～<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://im.marieclaire.com.tw/m800c533h100b0/assets/mc/202102/601790FB2EDCD1612157179.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fim.marieclaire.com.tw%2Fm800c533h100b0%2Fassets%2Fmc%2F202102%2F601790FB2EDCD1612157179.jpeg&h=4588c5d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n說到IKEA超人氣玩偶，絕對非「藍色鯊魚」BL&Aring;HAJ填充玩具莫屬，而現在出現了全新勁敵，那就是一隻高達100公分的棕熊玩偶！超萌魅力引起日本Twitter網友熱烈討論<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://im.marieclaire.com.tw/m800c533h100b0/assets/mc/202102/60179174792C41612157300.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fim.marieclaire.com.tw%2Fm800c533h100b0%2Fassets%2Fmc%2F202102%2F60179174792C41612157300.jpeg&h=6690e77d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://im.marieclaire.com.tw/m800c533h100b0/assets/mc/202102/6017914C5A57A1612157260.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fim.marieclaire.com.tw%2Fm800c533h100b0%2Fassets%2Fmc%2F202102%2F6017914C5A57A1612157260.jpeg&h=18eba635&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而日本推特網友日前上傳逛IKEA時的照片，看到四隻棕熊癱軟坐在餐桌上，宛如喝醉般恣意趴睡或發懶，配上垂垂的眼睛，像是被工作榨乾的你我，散發濃厚厭世氛圍，立刻引起網友熱論、紛紛PO出在賣場中看到的有趣畫面，使這隻棕熊玩偶成為爆紅人物。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://im.marieclaire.com.tw/m800c533h100b0/assets/mc/202102/6017922D6DC3B1612157485.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fim.marieclaire.com.tw%2Fm800c533h100b0%2Fassets%2Fmc%2F202102%2F6017922D6DC3B1612157485.jpeg&h=02b373ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.marieclaire.com.tw/share/fb/55166/c24d82/ps\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2